{"tid":2100840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【賭王設靈】靈堂外自稱是何鴻燊親女 周女士：一出世俾人抱去山旮旯","createTime":"2020-07-09T10:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T10:38:16.000Z","uid":212884,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a878061c9ebf208a0520da541b4c255a72f2d7fa","tid":2100840,"uid":212884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:28:42.000Z","msg":"年約60歲、略帶鄉音的周女士表示：「我細個俾佢抱咗去山旮旯湊大&hellip;&hellip;係佢契女呀，都屬於親女呀。」問她何人湊大她時，她重複說：「我細個俾佢送咗去山旮旯。」<br />\n<br />\n其後，有個自稱是周女士丈夫的譚姓男士，聲稱自己是譚詠麟細佬，他又指自己因為得閒，才陪太太前來向賭王致祭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AG9tSqG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAG9tSqG.jpg&h=182e3961&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bS8KqLG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbS8KqLG.jpg&h=6974aff3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DBxrD5H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDBxrD5H.jpg&h=5dfd0ff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200709/LCZQXATAJ5DS7TOAXMDE7YXDL4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200709%2FLCZQXATAJ5DS7TOAXMDE7YXDL4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmvaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=90fc3c27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200709%2FLCZQXATAJ5DS7TOAXMDE7YXDL4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=ebefb050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200709/LCZQXATAJ5DS7TOAXMDE7YXDL4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm